      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.z8iOan4RJXYvVhit]{Exocortex Mods (Ex)}</p>\n<p><span>Once per day as a standard action, your exocortex can turn you invisible for 10 minutes, as per the <em>invisibility&nbsp;</em></span>spell. If it makes an attack during this time, the invisibility ends. Your Exocortex can spend 2 Resolve Points to use this ability again on the same day. Your Exocortex must have the reactive camouflage mod to select this.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.0bdUwHd54TkeC62Z]{Exocortex Mod, Reactive Camoflage (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.YDXegEus8p0BnsH1]{Invisibility}</p>"
